From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000001 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: PanicOS <panicos@example.com>
Date: Thu, 01 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] rockchip: add rk3326-handheld defconfig and common DTS

Add ROCKNIX's rk3326-handheld_defconfig (targeting a generic handheld
rk3326 board) and the supporting rk3326-common-handheld.dts.

Sourced from ROCKNIX https://github.com/ROCKNIX/distribution
at the pinned SHA in soc/rockchip-rk3326/source.manifest.v2.
---
 configs/rk3326-handheld_defconfig                                  | 127 ++++
 dts/upstream/src/arm64/rockchip/rk3326-common-handheld.dts         | 398 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 2 files changed, 525 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 configs/rk3326-handheld_defconfig
 create mode 100644 dts/upstream/src/arm64/rockchip/rk3326-common-handheld.dts

diff --git a/configs/rk3326-handheld_defconfig b/configs/rk3326-handheld_defconfig
new file mode 100644
index 0000000000..72f1fb7ca9d58251f01984dc0eedb7cf558ce648
--- /dev/null
+++ b/configs/rk3326-handheld_defconfig
@@ -0,0 +1,127 @@
+CONFIG_ARM=y
+CONFIG_SKIP_LOWLEVEL_INIT=y
+CONFIG_COUNTER_FREQUENCY=24000000
+CONFIG_ARCH_ROCKCHIP=y
+CONFIG_NR_DRAM_BANKS=1
